# =============================================
# DEPLOYMENT INSTRUCTIONS
# =============================================

# After deploying smart contracts, update the following variables:
# 1. VITE_DISASTER_RELIEF_CONTRACT="0x..." (from deployment output)
# 2. VITE_MOCK_USDC_CONTRACT="0x..." (from deployment output)
# 3. Set up Pinata account and update IPFS credentials
# 4. Update CSP headers in public/_headers file with contract addresses

# For production deployment:
# 1. Set VITE_NODE_ENV="production"
# 2. Set VITE_DEBUG_MODE="false"
# 3. Update VITE_CHAIN_ID=43114 for mainnet
# 4. Update RPC and explorer URLs for mainnet
# 5. Remove or secure debug features
